nel%20and%20using%20pressurised%20vehicles%2C%20trains%20travelling%20along%20the%20structure%20could%20theoretically%20reach%20speeds%20of%20more%20than%203%2C000%20mph%2C%20making%20the%20journey%20between%20London%20and%20New%20York%20barely%20an%20hour%20long.%20This%20is%20because%20trains%20would%20not%20face%20any%20air%20resistance%20within%20the%20tunnel%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20reach%20higher%20speeds%20than%20conventional%20trains.%20This%20design%2C%20which%20has%20seen%20new%20development%20in%20Indian%20transportation%2C%20is%20sometimes%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Bhyperloop.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECutting%20the%20intercontinental%20journey%20down%20to%20a%20matter%20of%20minutes%20means%20that%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20the%20Transatlantic%20Tunnel%20justifies%20the%20hefty%20price%20tag%20that%20undersea%20construction%20comes%20with%2C%20as%20it%20would%20become%20significantly%20more%20efficient%20and%20environmentally%20friendly%20than%20flying.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733885220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Ftqj3n2so_tunnel-_625x300_11_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fnew-york-from-london-in-1-hour-bold-trans-atlantic-train-tunnel-proposal-resurfaces-7220735%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ambitious%20concept%20of%20a%20Transatlantic%20Tunnel%20connecting%20New%20York%20and%20London%20has%20resurfaced%2C%20promising%20travel%20between%20the%20cities%20in%20under%20an%20hour.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fnew-york-from-london-in-1-hour-bold-trans-atlantic-train-tunnel-proposal-resurfaces-7220735%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20are%20India's%20choices%20for%20bowling%20line-up%20in%20Brisbane%20Test%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733885095000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2F