al-navy-drone-landing-on-prince-of-wales-aircraft-carrier-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFleet%20Air%20Arm%3C%2Fa%3E%20developed%20three%20prototypes%20as%20part%20of%20their%20efforts%20to%20create%20a%20fighter%20jet%20that%20could%20operate%20aboard%20carriers%2C%20as%20well%20as%20new%20deck-landing%20techniques.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20flight%20trials%20for%20the%20Sea%20Vampire%20prototype%20took%20place%20off%20the%20south%20coast%20of%20England.%20The%20Sea%20Vampire%20trial%20planned%20to%20have%20the%20aircraft%20land%20on%20the%20Ocean's%20flight%20deck%20at%2095%20mph%2C%20though%20strong%20gusts%20caused%20the%20plane%20to%20land%20faster%20than%20anticipated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20aircraft's%20tail-down%20angle%20and%20the%20pitching%20of%20the%20carrier's%20flight%20deck%2C%20the%20plane's%20trailing%20edge%20wing%20flaps%20hit%20the%20deck%2C%20breaking%20their%20hinges%20upon%20landing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%2C%20however%2C%20was%20determined%20to%20pull%20off%20a%20perfect%20landing.%20He%20made%20several%20more%20takeoffs%20and%20landings%20on%20the%20Ocean%2C%20accomplishing%20the%20feat%20on%20the%20fourth%20try%20despite%20the%20initial%20damage%20to%20the%20Sea%20Vampire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarrier%20landings%20were%20considered%20some%20of%20the%20most%20challenging%20maneuvers%20at%20the%20time%2C%20so%20demonstrating%20that%20higher-speed%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efighter%20jets%20could%20safely%20land%20marked%20a%20turning%20point%20in%20naval%20aviation.%20The%20first%20successful%20jet-powered%20carrier%20landing%20catalyzed%20the%20innovation%20of%20carrier%20technology%20and%20design%20to%20better%20accommodate%20jet%20aircraft%2C%20including%20angled%20flight%20decks%2C%20steam-powered%20aircraft%20catapults%2C%20and%20more%20advanced%20arresting%20gear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20advancements%20ushered%20in%20a%20new%20era%2C%20expanding%20and%20enhancing%20the%20capabilities%20of%20both%20the%20flattops%20and%20t