6quot%3B%20but%20that%20a%20strong%20Q4%20could%20help%20the%20company%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20written%20statement%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20data%20came%20from%20a%20study%20tracking%20brand%20awareness%20during%20the%20brand%20transition%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-bard-gemini-ai-generative-llm-alphabet-rebrand-duet-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BDuet%20AI%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3BGemini%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20year%20and%20called%20the%20data%20%26quot%3Bold%20and%20obsolete.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20time%20since%2C%20we've%20brought%20Gemini%20for%20Workspace%20to%20millions%20more%20customers%20and%20made%20significant%2C%20double-digit%20gains%20across%20key%20categories%2C%20including%20familiarity%2C%20future%20consideration%2C%20and%20usage.%20We're%20very%20pleased%20with%20our%20momentum%20and%20are%20encouraged%20by%20all%20the%20great%20feedback%20we%20are%20getting%20from%20our%20users%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20internal%20data%20tracked%20Gemini's%20brand%20strength%20across%20commercial%2C%20consumer%2C%20and%20executive%20groups.%20In%20the%20US%20commercial%20group%2C%20Gemini%20scored%20lower%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-ai-artificial-intelligence-bet-doubts-marc-benioff-satya-nadella-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%20Copilot%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20ChatGPT%20across%20four%20categories%3A%20familiarity%2C%20consideration%2C%20usage%2C%20and%20paid%20usage%2C%20one%20slide%20showed.%20Paid%20usage%20was%20measured%20at%2022%25%2C%2016%20points%20lower%20than%20Copilot%20and%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20for%20the%20UK%20in%20the%20commercial%20group%20also%20showed%20Gemini%20mostly%20behind%20its%20rivals%2C%20although%20it%20scored%20slightly%20higher%20than%20Copilot%20in%20paid%20usage.%20In%20Brazil%