2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fmicrosoft-investors-reject-bitcoin-crypto-investment-proposal-michael-saylor-microstrategy-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22MicroStrategy%20CEO%20Michael%20Saylor%20had%20pitched%20Microsoft's%20board%20on%20investing%20in%20bitcoin.%20Investors%20voted%20against%20the%20proposal%20on%20Thursday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22fdemott%40insider.com%20(Filip%20De%20Mott)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A281%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fmicrosoft-investors-reject-bitcoin-crypto-investment-proposal-michael-saylor-microstrategy-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Scientists%20From%20India%2C%20A%20Telescope%20In%20Chile%2C%20And%20An%20Astronomical%20Discovery%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAstronomers%20from%20India%20have%20made%20an%20intriguing%20discovery%20in%20a%20unique%20tri-star%20solar%20system%20located%20489%20light%20years%20from%20Earth.%20The%20discovery%20will%20help%20astrophysicists%20get%20a%20better%20understanding%20of%20planetary%20formations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAstronomers%20from%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Science%20Education%20and%20Research%20or%20NISER%20in%20Odisha%20have%20made%20the%20discovery%20using%20the%20advanced%20radio%20telescope%20in%20Chile's%20Atacama%20Desert.%20Their%20observations%2C%20sustained%20over%20a%20period%20of%20time%2C%20reveal%20fascinating%20insights%20into%20the%20complexities%20of%20planetary%20formation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three-star%20system%20that%20was%20being%20observed%20was%20the%20'GG%20Tau%20A'%20solar%20system%20which%20is%20in%20its%20nascent%20stage%20of%20planetary%20formations.%20The%20system%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20around%205%20million%20years%20old.%20What%20makes%20it%20unique%20is%20that%20there%20are%20three%20'Suns'%20with%20a%20massive%20protoplanetary%20disk%20-%20a%20rotating%20disk%20of%20gas%20and%20dust%20that%20forms%20around%20a%20young%20star%20and%20provides%20the%20materials%20for%20new%20planets%20to%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20the%20three%20stars%20orbit%20each%20other%2C%20the%20giant%20ring%20of%20gas%20and%20dust%2C%20which%20over%20time%20will%20form%20planets%2C%20get%20significantly%20altered%20due%20to%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20stars%20in%20their%20orbiting%20pattern%2C%20giving%20scientists%20fascinating%20insights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20THE%20INDIAN%20ASTRONOMERS%20HAVE%20DISCOVERED%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20of%20astronomers%20from%20NISER%20was%20led%20by%20scientist%20Liton%20Majumdar%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20visiting%20scientist%20at%20NASA.%20His%20area%20of%20specialisation%20is%20star%20and%20planetary%20formations%2C%20astrochemistry%2C%20and%20exoplanet%20studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20team%20and%20he%20have%20detected%20molecular%20emissions%20from%20the%20protoplanetary%20disk%20which%20are%20the%20fundamental%20building%20blocks%20of%20planets.%20These%20emissions%20were%20found%20to%20originate%20in%20the%20coldest%20and%20most%20dense%20regions%20of%20the%20star%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20carried%20out%20their%20research%20focusing%20on%20the%20coldest%20regions%20of%20the%20tri-star%20system%2C%20where%20temperatures%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20as%20low%20as%2016%20Kelvin%20or%C2%A0%20minus%20(-)257.15%20degrees%20Celsius%20-%20well%20below%20the%20freezing%20point%20of%20carbon%20monoxide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECarbon%20Monoxide%20is%20key%20for%20scientists%20to%20trace%20the%20mass%20of%20gas%20during%20the%20formation%20of%20planets.%20The%20chemical%20composition%20of%20carbon%20monoxide%20-%20CO%20-%20carries%20carbon%20and%20oxygen%2C%20and%20reacts%20with%20other%20gases%20to%20form%20compounds%20like%20CH4%20(methane).%20Its%20bright%20color%20helps%20astronomers%20model%20protoplanetary%20disks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EINSIGHTS%20FROM%20THE%20DISCOVERY%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20scientists%20have%20been%20studying%20single%20star%20solar%20systems%20like%20our%20own%2C%20and%20have%20also%20carried%20out%20research%20on%20binary%20star%20systems%20like%20Alpha%20Centauri%2C%20understanding%20the%20complexities%20of%20a%20tri-star%20system%20is%20unique.%20The%20GG%20Tau%20A%20star%20system%20being%20located%20in%20our%20cosmic%20neighbourhood%20also%20helps%20answer%20key%20questions%20in%20astrophysics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20helps%20understand%20the%20fundamental%20nature%20of%20planetary%20formation%20under%20the%20complications%20caused%20due%20to%20the%20gravitational%20force%20of%20three%20host%20stars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGravity%2C%20temperature%2C%20mass%20(energy)%2C%20pressure%2C%20and%20frequency%20are%20key%20aspects%20of%20physics%20and%20studying%20these%20in%20a%20three-star%20system%20gives%20scientists%20a%20challenge%20as%20well%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20make%20groundbreaking%20discoveries%20in%20such%20complex%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETHE%20RADIO%20TELESCOPE%20IN%20ATACAMA%20DESERT%2C%20CHILE%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20astronomers%20from%20India%20used%20the%20Atacama%20Pathfinder%20Experiment%20or%20APEX%20radio%20telescope%20-%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20telescopes%20on%20Earth%20-%20located%20at%20a%20height%20of%205%2C064%20meters%20above%20sea%20level%20in%20the%20Atacama%20desert%20in%20Chile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20facility%20is%20built%20and%20operated%20by%20three%20European%20research%20institutes%20-%20The%20European%20Southern%20Observatory%2C%20The%20Max%20Planck%20Institute%20for%20Radio%20Astronomy%2C%20and%20The%20Onsala%20Space%20Observatory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20APEX%20telescope%20is%20a%20modified%20ALMA%20(Atacama%20Large%20Millimeter%20Array)%20prototype%20antenna%20and%20is%20at%20the%20site%20of%20the%20ALMA%20observatory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ALMA%20telescope%2C%20also%20located%20in%20the%20Atacama%20Desert%20in%20Chile%2C%20is%20an%20astronomical%20interferometer%20of%2066%20radio%20telescopes%20which%20observe%20the%20electromagnetic%20radiation%20from%20space%20at%20millimeter%20and%20submillimeter%20wavelengths.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733862480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F3ndcp8gs_alma-telescope-chile-atacama-desert-youtube_625x300_10_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fscientists-from-india-a-telescope-in-chile-and-an-astronomical-discovery-7219190%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Astronomers%20from%20India%20have%20made%20an%20intriguing%20discovery%20in%20a%20unique%20tri-star%20solar%20system%20located%20489%20light%20years%20from%20Earth.%20The%20discovery%20will%20help%20astrophysicists%20get%20a%20better%20understanding%20of%20planetary%20formations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fscientists-from-india-a-telescope-in-chile-and-an-astronomical-discovery-7219190%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20hope%20Assad%20pays%20the%20price%2C%20says%20mother%20whose%20son's%20death%20inflamed%202011%20Syrian%20revolution%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733862290000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F0104%2Flive%2Ffb2ca6b0-b732-11ef-aff0-072ce821b6ab.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fckg9z3r2xp9o%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hamza%20al-Khatib%2C%2013%2C%20was%20arrested%20at%20a%202011%20anti-government%20rally%20and%20tortured%20-%20but%20Assad's%20downfall%20has%20not%20brought%20his%20family%20justice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A77%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fckg9z3r2xp9o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2