%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223695%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGhost%20guns%20can%20have%20a%20mix%20of%203D%20printed%20components%20and%20metal%20parts.%3Cp%3EYuki%20Iwamura%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPolice%20said%20they%20found%20a%20%26quot%3Bghost%20gun%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20UnitedHealthcare%20CEO%20shooting%20suspect.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGhost%20guns%20are%20untraceable%20firearms%20that%20can%20be%20assembled%20at%20home%2C%20raising%20safety%20concerns.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EElected%20officials%20are%20cracking%20down%20on%20the%20sale%20of%20such%20weapons%20to%20curb%20their%20accessibility.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPolice%20say%20a%20weapon%20they%20found%20on%20UnitedHealthcare%20CEO%20shooting%20suspect%20Luigi%20Mangione%20could%20be%20a%203D%20printed%20ghost%20gun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fghost-guns-order-online-diy-assemble-700-shootings-in-2021-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGhost%20guns%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20firearms%20assembled%20at%20home%20using%20parts%20that%20were%20purchased%20individually.%20Sometimes%2C%20those%20components%20are%20made%20using%20a%203D%20printer.%20It's%20legal%20to%20buy%20the%20parts%20and%20use%20them%20to%20make%20your%20own%20gun%2C%20but%20laws%20prohibit%20the%20sale%20or%20transfer%20of%20ghost%20guns%20to%20another%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMangione%20%26quot%3Bwas%20in%20possession%20of%20a%20ghost%20gun%20that%20had%20the%20capability%20of%20firing%20a%209mm%20round%2C%26quot%3B%20Joe%20Kenny%2C%20the%20New%20York%20Police%20Department's%20chief%20of%20detectives%2C%20told%20reporters%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Bmay%20have%20been%20made%20on%20a%203D%20printer%26quot%3B%3B%20there's%20no%20confirmation%20that%20it%20was%20the%20same%20gun%20used%20to%20kill%20Brian%20Thompson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMangione%20is%20being%20held%20without%20bail%2C%20and%20a%20lawyer%20for%20him%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20publicly%20identified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20authorities%20and%20gun%20safety%20groups%20have%20raised%20concerns%20about%20ghost%20guns%2C%20which%20are%20accessible%20online%20in%20kits.%20More%20than%2025%2C000%20privately%20made%20firearms%20were%20recovered%20by%20US%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20in%202022%2C%20according%20to%20the%20DOJ.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20New%20York%20City%20officials%20filed%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nyc.gov%2Foffice-of-the-mayor%2Fnews%2F748-22%2Fmayor-adams-stops-additional-ghost-gun-retailer-selling-ghost-gun-kits-nyc-residents%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elawsuit%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20five%20ghost%20gun%20retailers%20over%20their%20sales%20to%20residents.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravel-new-york-mayor-eric-adam-alleged-accepted-court-documents-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMayor%20Eric%20Adams%3C%2Fa%3E%20eventually%20came%20to%20an%20agreement%20with%20at%20least%20four%20of%20the%20companies%20that%20would%20stop%20the%20sale%20of%20ghost%20guns%20in%20NYC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20if%20the%20firearm%20Pennsylvania%20police%20say%20they%20recovered%20from%20Mangione%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bradyunited.org%2Fresources%2Fissues%2Fwhat-are-ghost-guns%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eis%20technically%20a%20ghost%20gun%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20Kris%20Brown%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20gun%20safety%20group%20Brady.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey'll%20know%20for%20sure%20once%20investigators%20examine%20the%20weapon%20to%20see%20if%20any%20of%20its%20component%20parts%20have%20serial%20numbers.%20Only%20if%20there%20are%20no%20serial%20numbers%20is%20it%20a%20ghost%20gun%2C%20meaning%20entirely%20unregulated%20and%20untraceable%2C%20Brown%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMangione%20may%20have%20printed%20the%20plastic%20portions%20of