%20problems%20of%20the%20country's%20metro%20cities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDelhi%20has%20four%20mountains%20of%20municipal%20garbage.%20Now%2C%20we%20have%20used%2080%20lakh%20tons%20of%20municipal%20garbage%20in%20road%20construction%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV%20at%20the%20special%20Auto%20Conclave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20cases%20in%20point%2C%20he%20named%20a%20number%20of%20highways%20in%20western%20and%20northern%20India%20--%20the%20Mumbai-Delhi%20Express%20highway%2C%20Ahmedabad-Vadodara%20highway%2C%20the%20Ahmedabad%20Dholera%20highway%20and%20also%20in%20roads%20in%20parts%20of%20Chandigarh%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20to%20convert%20stubble%20into%20biofuel%20is%20also%20going%20ahead%20full%20steam%2C%20he%20said.%20This%20will%20also%20take%20care%20of%20the%20massive%20pollution%20issue%2C%20especially%20the%20haze%20that%20chokes%20north%20India%20every%20winter.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BWe%20have%20400%20projects%20in%20the%20process%20for%20which%2060%20have%20already%20started%20and%20they%20are%20making%20bio-CNG%20from%20parali%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20in%20Panipat%2C%20there%20is%20a%20project%20of%20IndianOil%20where%20they%20are%20making%201%20lakh%20litres%20of%20bio-ethanol%20from%20rice%20stalks%20or%20parali%2C%20150%20tonnes%20of%20bio%20vitamins%20and%2078%2C000%20tons%20per%20year%20of%20aviation%20fuel%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20underscoring%20that%20it%20is%20a%20classic%20case%20of%20%26quot%3Bwaste%20to%20wealth%26quot%3B%20generation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20he%20said%2C%20would%20also%20reduce%20reduce%20import%20bill%20and%20pollution%20and%20establishes%20an%20economic%20point%20of%20view%20of%20being%20%26quot%3Batmanirbhar%26quot%3B%20(self%20reliant).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20burning%20of%20parali%2C%20the%20minister%20said%2C%20has%20gone%20down%20by%2040%20per%20cent%20and%20will%20be%20down%20to%2