A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fomnicom-s-interpublic-group-buy-to-make-it-india-s-second-largest-ad-firm-124121001033_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dungeons%2C%20Torture%20Chambers%20Exposed%20After%20Assad's%20Fall%20In%20Syria%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESyrians%20lived%20in%20terror%20for%20decades%20of%20what%20went%20on%20behind%20the%20concrete%20walls%20of%20Damascus's%20security%20compound.%20Now%20the%20Assad%20dynasty%20has%20been%20toppled%2C%20its%20dungeons%20and%20torture%20chambers%20are%20giving%20up%20their%20secrets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERebel%20fighters%20stand%20guard%20at%20the%20entrances%20to%20the%20forbidden%20city%20in%20the%20capital's%20Kafr%20Sousa%20district%2C%20where%20the%20feared%20security%20services%20had%20their%20headquarters%20alongside%20government%20offices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20myriad%20of%20different%20agencies%20which%20kept%20tabs%20on%20the%20lives%20of%20ordinary%20Syrians%20each%20operated%20their%20own%20underground%20prisons%20and%20interrogation%20chambers%20inside%20the%20walled%20defence%20ministry%20compound.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESyrians%20lived%20in%20fear%20of%20being%20summoned%20for%20a%20round%20of%20questioning%20from%20which%20they%20might%20never%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAFP%20found%20first%20responder%20Sleiman%20Kahwaji%20wandering%20around%20the%20complex%20this%20week%20trying%20to%20locate%20the%20building%20where%20he%20was%20questioned%20and%20then%20detained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20was%20still%20at%20secondary%20school%20when%20he%20was%20arrested%20in%202014%20on%20suspicion%20of%20%26quot%3Bterrorism%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20frequent%20allegation%20under%20the%20rule%20of%20now%20toppled%20president%20Bashar%20al-Assad%2C%20who%20brooked%20no%20dissent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'My%20dear%20mother'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20spent%2055%20days%20underground%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20were%2055%20of%20us%20in%20that%20dungeon.%20Two%20died%2C%20one%20from%20diabetes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScribbled%20graffiti%20left%20by%20the%20prisoners%20are%20barely%20legible%20on%20the%20walls%20amid%20the%20darkness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20dear%20mother%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20had%20scribbled%2C%20probably%20in%20his%20own%20blood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cells%20that%20were%20used%20for%20solitary%20confinement%20are%20so%20small%20there%20isn't%20even%20space%20to%20lie%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%2080%20prisoners%20per%20cell%20were%20crammed%20into%20the%20larger%20ones%2C%20forcing%20inmates%20to%20take%20turns%20to%20sleep%2C%20recalls%20another%20former%20detainee%20Thaer%20Mustafa%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20for%20alleged%20desertion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20remaining%20prisoners%20were%20freed%20on%20Sunday%20after%20their%20captors%20fled%20as%20the%20rebels%20swept%20into%20Damascus%20capping%20the%20lightning%20offensive%20they%20launched%20late%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20large%20crowd%20broke%20into%20the%20security%20zone%20and%20ransacked%20the%20sprawling%20offices%20on%20the%20upper%20floors%20of%20the%20complex.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20intelligence%20files%20lay%20abandoned%2C%20many%20of%20them%20scattered%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20detailing%20the%20activities%20of%20ordinary%20citizens%20subjected%20to%20draconian%20surveillance%20by%20security%20service%20agents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20handwritten%20document%20lists%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20prisoners%20held%20on%20suspicion%20of%20membership%20of%20the%20Muslim%20Brotherhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sunni%20Islamist%20group%20was%20anathema%20to%20the%20Assad%20clan%20who%20are%20members%20of%20Syria's%20Alawite%20minority%2C%20followers%20of%20an%20offshoot%20of%20Shiite%20Islam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrotherhood%20membership%20became%20punishable%20by%20death%20since%201980%20two%20years%20before%20Assad's%20father%20and%20predecessor%20Hafez%20ordered%20the%20army%20to%20crush%20its%20insurgency%20with%20an%20assault%20on%20the%20central%20city%20of%20Hama%20which%20killed%20between%2010%2C000%20and%2040%2C000%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlongside%20each%20prisoner's%20name%20and%20date%20of%20birth%2C%20the%20security%20services%20noted%20the%20details%20of%20their%20detention%20and%20interrogation%2C%20and%20whether%20and%20when%20they%20had%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20abandoned%20file%20details%20the%20detention%20of%20a%20Briton%20of%20Syrian%20origin%2C%20who%20was%20subjected%20to%20a%20lie%20detector%20test%20over%20allegations%20he%20was%20working%20for%20British%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPaid%20informers%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%2C%20dated%20this%20January%2C%20details%20the%20investigation%20into%20a%20bomb%20attack%20on%20the%20Mazzeh%20neighbourhood%20of%20Damascus%2C%20in%20which%20an%20Iraqi%20was%20wounded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENothing%20was%20considered%20too%20trivial%20to%20escape%20the%20security%20services'%20attention.%20There%20are%20files%20recording%20the%20activities%20of%20ordinary%20citizens%20as%20well%20as%20journalists%20and%20religious%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20even%20government%20ministers%20were%20immune.%20On%20a%20list%20of%20members%20of%20Assad's%20government%2C%20a%20security%20service%20agent%20has%20carefully%20noted%20the%20confession%20of%20each%20minister%20--%20Sunni%20or%20Alawite%2C%20Christian%20or%20Druze.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20security%20services%20operated%20vast%20networks%20of%20paid%20informers%2C%20who%20provided%20the%20tiniest%20details%20of%20people's%20daily%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFamilies%20have%20been%20arriving%20at%20the%20gates%20of%20the%20Damascus%20security%20zone%20since%20Saturday%2C%20desperately%20seeking%20word%20on%20the%20fate%20of%20their%20missing%20loved%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20come%20af