-in-fortified-courtroom-as-he-calls-corruption-claims-absurd-13270892%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fbenjamin-netanyahu-gives-evidence-in-fortified-courtroom-as-he-calls-corruption-claims-absurd-13270892%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ex-Pacer%2C%20Once%20Victim%20Of%20A%20Sachin%20Rampage%2C%20Is%20Now%20A%20Painter%20In%20Australia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Zimbabwe%20fast%20bowler%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Henry%20Olonga%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F335-henry-olonga-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHenry%20Olonga%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20someone%20remembered%20fondly%20by%20Indians%2C%20for%20he%20was%20the%20victim%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sachin%20Tendulkar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F14-sachin-tendulkar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESachin%20Tendulkar%3C%2Fa%3E%20rampage%20in%201998.%20Playing%20the%20final%20of%20a%20triangular%20series%20between%20India%2C%20Zimbabwe%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Tendulkar%20smashed%20124%20off%2092%20balls%2C%20taking%20Olonga%20to%20the%20cleaners.%20Over%2025%20years%20later%2C%20however%2C%20Olonga's%20life%20has%20taken%20an%20unprecedented%20turn.%20In%202019%2C%20Olonga%20went%20viral%20as%20he%20wowed%20judges%20in%20'The%20Voice%20Australia'%20singing%20competition.%20Now%2C%20Olonga%20is%20a%20part-time%20painter%20for%20social%20causes%2C%20and%20was%20present%20during%20the%20second%20Test%20between%20India%20and%20Australia%20at%20Adelaide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOlonga%20has%20lived%20Down%20Under%20since%202015%2C%20and%20now%20plies%20his%20trade%20as%20a%20painter%2C%20casual%20coach%20and%20even%20as%20an%20umpire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20love%20Australia.%20I%20am%20married%20to%20an%20Australian%20wife%20and%20I%20have%20got%20two%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20Olonga%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsportstar.thehindu.com%2Fcricket%2Fhenry-olonga-interview-zimbabwe-india-sachin-tendulkar-bumrah-news%2Farticle68959162.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESportstar%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20his%20foray%20into%20the%20world%20of%20art%2C%20Olonga%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20always%20had%20that%20soft%20side%20and%20I%20never%20saw%20it%20as%20different%20or%20odd.%20I%20always%20liked%20variety.%20I%20get%20bored%20doing%20one%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOlonga%20was%20present%20at%20the%20Adelaide%20Oval%20during%20the%20second%20Test%20of%20the%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy.%20He%20had%20been%20seen%20painting%20a%20cricket%20stadium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOlonga%20last%20played%20for%20Zimbabwe%20in%20the%202003%20ODI%20World%20Cup%2C%20after%20which%20his%20stance%20on%20political%20atrocities%20in%20Zimbabwe%20led%20to%20his%20departure%20from%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20not%20actively%20involved%20with%20cricket%2C%20Olonga%20still%20keeps%20up%20with%20the%20game%2C%20and%20is%20particularly%20fond%20of%20India's%20pace%20spearhead%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jasprit%20Bumrah%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1724-jasprit-bumrah-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20even%20reserving%20a%20high%20compliment%20for%20the%2031-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B(Jasprit)%20Bumrah%20is%20the%20best%20bowler%2C%20has%20got%20a%20bit%20of%20hyper-extension%2C%20which%20gives%20him%20a%20crack.%20He%20reminds%20me%20of%20Wasim%20(Akram)%20of%20the%20short%20run-up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMugabe%20also%20reminisced%20about%20Tendulkar's%20rampage%20against%20Zimbabwe%2C%20as%20India%20won%20the%20triangular%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20remembers%20because%20it%20is%20on%20YouTube.%20I%20got%20him%20(Tendulkar)%20out%20and%20then%20in%20the%20final%2C%20he%20went%20crazy%2C%20I%20went%20for%20plenty%20of%20runs%20(6-0-50-0)%20and%20he%20smashed%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Olonga%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733836500000%