20panel%20made%20from%20wood%20strands%20that%20are%20bonded%20together%20with%20resin%2C%20they%20add%20a%20bold%20dynamic%20to%20the%20space.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20the%20material%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Aameer%20Chauhan%2C%20Sustainability%20Manager%20at%20Edifice%20Consultant%20Pvt%20Ltd%2C%20an%20award-winning%20architecture%20design%20firm%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9COrient%20stranded%20board%20(OSB)%20has%20a%20low%20embodied%20carbon%20value%20and%20can%20be%20easily%20recycled%20into%20similar%20panels%20at%20the%20end%20of%20its%20life%20cycle.%20This%20makes%20it%20a%20sustainable%20and%20convenient%20material%20to%20use.%E2%80%9D%20Edifice%C2%A0heroed%20the%20material%20in%20one%20of%20its%20studio%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20choice%20was%20actually%20serendipitous%2C%20he%20smiles.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20limited%20options%20for%20modifying%20the%20existing%20walls%2C%20and%20OSB%20proved%20invaluable%20due%20to%20its%20easy%20and%20quick%20installation%20system.%E2%80%9D%20What%20the%20team%20also%20discovered%20during%20the%20project%2C%20was%20that%20the%20material%20boasted%20excellent%20acoustical%20properties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-3-1733297952.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Orient%20stranded%20boards%20are%20a%20type%20of%20engineered%20wood%20panel%20made%20from%20wood%20strands%20that%20are%20bonded%20together%20with%20resin%2C%20they%20add%20a%20bold%20dynamic%20to%20the%20space%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-3-1733297952.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-3-1733297952-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-3-1733297952-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-3-1733297952-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fsustainable-architecture-3-1733297952-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-386131%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOrient%20stranded%20boards%20are%20a%20type%20of%20engineered%20wood%20panel%20made%20from%20wood%20strands%20that%20are%20bonded%20together%20with%20resin.%20They%20add%20a%20bold%20dynamic%20to%20the%20space%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Edifice%20Consultant%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUsing%20OSB%20wall%20panels%20helped%20us%20nullify%20the%20unwanted%20refraction%20and%20reverberation%20in%20the%20studio.%20Since%20the%20OSB%20panels%20are%20not%20as%20highly%20compressed%20as%20plywood%20they%20are%20excellent%20sound%20absorbers%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aameer%20adds.%20But%20the%20real%20magic%20lies%20in%20the%20matrix.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20raw%20finish%20of%20%5BOSB%E2%80%99s%5D%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F316563%2Ftamil-nadu-sustsainable-home-with-plastic-bottles-and-mud-chuzi-vinu-daniel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewood%20strand%20composition%20%3C%2Fa%3Eadds%20a%20subtle%20texture%20to%20the%20overall%20monochromatic%2C%20industrial-themed%20office%20space.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArchitects%2C%20take%20notes%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20While%20OSB%20does%20manage%20to%20lend%20some%20bespoke%20detailing%20to%20the%20building%2C%20it%20